en.hi.dtsapp.model

Class Tour

  • java.lang.Object
    • en.hi.dtsapp.model.Tour

  • public class Tour
extends java.lang.Object
    Class Objectives: A Java object that represents a line from the Tour SQL Table. The only none-final String which has a setter is travelers which represents the number of travelers signed up for that Tour. setTravelers() and addTravelers() do not affect the values in the database they do however return true if update was successful, suggesting that the user may continue to update the booking in the DB using the class BookingDAO.java
